00:38:23.880 --> 00:38:25.400
Ngunit kung pipilitin mo,

00:38:25.400 --> 00:38:26.560
May isa yata.

00:38:27.040 --> 00:38:27.760
ano?

00:38:28.720 --> 00:38:29.840
Na ikaw ay lahat ng lakas.

00:38:32.840 --> 00:38:34.840
Oo, talaga.

00:38:34.880 --> 00:38:35.520
Sige.

00:38:36.280 --> 00:38:37.000
Tumigil ka

00:38:37.000 --> 00:38:37.880
pag-aliw sa sarili.

00:38:37.880 --> 00:38:38.440
Hayaan mong sabihin ko sa iyo,

00:38:38.440 --> 00:38:40.600
lahat ng tao may pagkukulang,

00:38:40.880 --> 00:38:43.320
at lahat ay may kalakasan.

00:38:44.240 --> 00:38:45.560
Ang mga tao sa paligid mo...

00:38:45.880 --> 00:38:47.640
Depende ito kung nakikita nila ang iyong mga kapintasan

00:38:47.640 --> 00:38:48.760
o ang iyong mga lakas.

00:38:49.520 --> 00:38:50.240
Ngunit sa tingin ko Cheng Man

00:38:50.240 --> 00:38:51.360
ay palaging nakikita ang iyong mga lakas.

00:40:44.120 --> 00:40:45.560
Bakit mo ako tinatawag?

00:40:46.760 --> 00:40:47.760
Nasaan ang iyong balbas?

00:40:48.440 --> 00:40:50.200
Ang gwapo mo kung wala ka.

00:40:51.240 --> 00:40:52.320
May nakita akong plastic bag.

00:40:54.160 --> 00:40:54.960
Umihip ang hangin

00:40:55.520 --> 00:40:56.760
at lumipad ito sa langit.

00:40:58.160 --> 00:40:59.680
Kaliwa, pagkatapos ay kanan,

00:41:00.080 --> 00:41:01.280
pataas, pagkatapos ay pababa.

00:41:03.840 --> 00:41:04.840
iniisip ko,

00:41:06.960 --> 00:41:07.720
alam ba nito

00:41:07.720 --> 00:41:08.920
na ito ay lumilipad

00:41:10.240 --> 00:41:11.000
dahil sa hangin,

00:41:11.840 --> 00:41:14.120
o iniisip ba nito

00:41:14.120 --> 00:41:15.240
kaya niyang lumipad mag-isa?

00:41:17.920 --> 00:41:18.960
Kapag huminto ang hangin,

00:41:20.560 --> 00:41:21.800
bumagsak ang bag sa lupa

00:41:23.320 --> 00:41:25.120
at natatapakan.

00:41:27.760 --> 00:41:29.200
Walang nagmamalasakit dito,

00:41:30.880 --> 00:41:33.440
kasi trash bag lang yan.

00:41:36.520 --> 00:41:37.320
anong mali?

00:41:39.440 --> 00:41:40.920
Maraming tao at pangyayari

00:41:42.200 --> 00:41:43.480
nagkataon lang na magkrus ang landas.

00:41:44.800 --> 00:41:46.520
Walang destiny.

00:41:49.480 --> 00:41:51.040
Ang iba ay bihirang nagmamalasakit.

00:41:52.800 --> 00:41:53.920
"Sumusunod sa agos"

00:41:53.920 --> 00:41:55.000
mukhang maganda,

00:41:56.440 --> 00:41:57.240
pero sa totoo lang

00:41:57.240 --> 00:41:58.760
umaanod na lang.

00:42:02.080 --> 00:42:03.080
sa tingin ko

00:42:04.320 --> 00:42:05.040
ang hangin

00:42:05.040 --> 00:42:06.280
ay wala sa kontrol ng bag.

00:42:06.800 --> 00:42:08.080
Ang tanging bagay na maaari nitong kontrolin

00:42:08.080 --> 00:42:08.880
ay iyon

00:42:09.920 --> 00:42:11.840
kahit gaano pa ito matapakan,

00:42:12.080 --> 00:42:13.760
hindi nito dapat makita ang sarili bilang isang trash bag.

00:42:15.200 --> 00:42:16.120
Yan ang susi.

00:42:16.360 --> 00:42:17.480
Sa mata ng iba,

00:42:17.560 --> 00:42:18.720
isa lang itong trash bag.

00:42:19.000 --> 00:42:19.920
Maaari itong humawak ng kahit ano.

00:42:21.240 --> 00:42:22.080
Oo naman.

00:42:22.960 --> 00:42:24.320
[Ngunit at least dapat alam nito]

00:42:24.320 --> 00:42:25.240
[kapaki-pakinabang pa rin.]

00:42:28.760 --> 00:42:29.840
[May sasabihin ako sa iyo.]

00:42:30.400 --> 00:42:31.320
[Kailan ka pa]

00:42:31.320 --> 00:42:32.360
[bumalik sa Canada?]

00:42:32.440 --> 00:42:33.680
[Kung hindi ka babalik kaagad,]

00:42:33.680 --> 00:42:34.360
[kapag bumalik ka]

00:42:34.360 --> 00:42:35.360
[Hindi mo ako makikita dito.]

00:42:35.760 --> 00:42:36.440
anong ginagawa mo

00:42:37.600 --> 00:42:38.480
[Nakapagdesisyon na ako.]

00:42:40.240 --> 00:42:41.120
[Tapos na akong gawin]

00:42:41.120 --> 00:42:42.240
[mga pagsasaayos sa Canada.]

00:42:42.280 --> 00:42:43.760
Walang kabuluhan sa akin.

00:42:44.360 --> 00:42:45.400
Babalik ako sa paggawa ng pelikula,

00:42:46.440 --> 00:42:47.480
dahil ito ay

00:42:48.200 --> 00:42:49.800
ang tanging bagay sa aking buhay

00:42:49.800 --> 00:42:51.000
na tunay na nagpapasaya sa akin.

00:42:52.840 --> 00:42:54.240
[Wala akong pakialam kung ano ang tingin nila sa akin.]

00:42:54.600 --> 00:42:55.240
[Kung iniisip nila]

00:42:55.240 --> 00:42:56.480
[Hindi ako magaling dati,]

00:42:57.160 --> 00:42:58.240
Kaya kong magsimula ulit.

00:42:59.320 --> 00:43:00.800
Alinmang paraan, gagawa ako

00:43:00.800 --> 00:43:01.840
isang mahusay na pelikula.

00:43:05.240 --> 00:43:06.400
[Binabati kita, Zhihao.]

00:43:07.520 --> 00:43:09.200
Kaya mo na ulit ang sarili mo.

00:43:09.600 --> 00:43:10.200
Maaari mong gawin

00:43:10.200 --> 00:43:11.440
ang mahal mo.

00:43:11.920 --> 00:43:13.160
Gawin mo lang!

00:43:16.800 --> 00:43:17.680
Ilang sandali pa,

00:43:18.640 --> 00:43:19.960
sa isang secondhand market,

00:43:20.160 --> 00:43:21.520
May nakita akong DVD player.

00:43:23.000 --> 00:43:24.040
Napaisip ako,

00:43:25.120 --> 00:43:26.520
[ngunit binili ko ito.]

00:43:27.640 --> 00:43:28.880
[Alam mo kung ano ang iniisip ko?]

00:43:29.520 --> 00:43:30.880
Noon,

00:43:31.440 --> 00:43:33.000
mayroon kaming ikaw, ako, at ang mga DVD,

00:43:33.760 --> 00:43:35.000
ngunit walang DVD player.

00:43:36.040 --> 00:43:38.720
Ngayon ay mayroon ako, ang mga DVD,

00:43:38.720 --> 00:43:39.720
at isang DVD player,

00:43:41.040 --> 00:43:41.920
pero hindi ikaw.

00:43:46.720 --> 00:43:47.280
ayos lang.

00:43:48.000 --> 00:43:49.360
Kapag ang iyong pelikula

00:43:49.800 --> 00:43:50.720
nanalo sa pinakamalaking

00:43:50.720 --> 00:43:52.320
internasyonal na parangal,

00:43:52.320 --> 00:43:53.800
anyayahan mo ako at doon ako.

00:43:54.080 --> 00:43:55.800
Pupunta ako sa premiere!

00:43:58.400 --> 00:44:00.400
Ito ay isang deal.

00:44:02.080 --> 00:44:03.080
Okay, Zhihao.

00:44:03.960 --> 00:44:04.760
pakakawalan na kita.

00:44:04.760 --> 00:44:05.960
Magtrabaho sa iyong script.

00:44:08.040 --> 00:44:08.640
Zhihao,

00:44:10.360 --> 00:44:11.640
matawagan ka

00:44:12.600 --> 00:44:13.640
nagpapasaya talaga sa akin.

00:44:14.560 --> 00:44:15.520
[Pagkuha ng iyong tawag]

00:44:15.520 --> 00:44:16.400
[Nagpapasaya rin ako ng totoo.]

00:44:18.240 --> 00:44:18.880
Nakuha mo na ito.

